{"tid":299584,"cid":8,"subCid":0,"title":"真心推介 只有我不存在的城市 依套動畫","createTime":"2017-06-27T08:13:37.000Z","updateTime":"2017-06-27T08:41:05.000Z","uid":49979,"like":0,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"bff18e8931849b4eb9e6f2335228b2e93d15123a","tid":299584,"uid":49979,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-27T08:13:37.000Z","msg":"一直好鍾意睇依d得十幾集既小品<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n我唔係唔鍾意睇火影依d大作 只係6百幾7百集入邊<br />\n<br />\n精彩既都唔知有冇3分1<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />  其他都係回憶同loop跳樹林<br />\n<br />\n畢竟世界觀做到咁撚大 有時有d野都唔怪得依d大作<br />\n<br />\n但係只有我不存在的城市唔同<br />\n<br />\n畫質 劇情 深度 張力 冇一樣比唔上大作<br />\n<br />\n節奏控制仲要做得好好多 唔會dum波鐘<br />\n<br />\n睇完十幾集就好似飲左杯靚咖啡咁<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n其他我會睇依套野都係因為之前一個講神作但係唔紅既動畫post<br />\n<br />\n所以係到睇下有冇其他好作推介<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"030f15b3a7f582991814008f2c62764e17450e94","tid":299584,"uid":121771,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-27T08:36:16.000Z","msg":"我覺得前半部係神作 後半部稍為欠佳 但係整體上都係一套好好嘅動畫"},{"pid":"b523c49ed9ca94050644672a1cdeb4a506130f84","tid":299584,"uid":36443,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-27T08:41:05.000Z","msg":"我都好鍾意呢套<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kiss.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 要懸疑有懸疑，要感動有感動，雖然凶手好明顯<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n不過動畫結尾爛左<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/chicken.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}